di 01 au dimanche 03 mai.<\/p><p>Paris Lyon &lt;-&gt; Melun interrompu.<br><br>Tous les trains de la ligne R seront d&#233;tourn&#233;s par Corbeil-Essonnes et auront pour <b>origine et terminus la gare de Juvisy.<\/b><\/p><p>Pr&#233;voir un allongement de temps de trajet.<\/p><p><b>Pour rejoindre Paris, nous vous conseillons de prendre un train de la ligne C en correspondance &#224; Juvisy.<\/b><\/p><p>Les horaires du calculateur d'itin&#233;raire tiennent compte des travaux.<\/p><p>Motif : travaux sur le r&#233;seau ferroviaire.<\/p>","shortMessage":"Arrêt(s) non desservi(s)","impactedSections":[{"lineId":"line:IDFM:C01731","from":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:73626","name":"Gare de Lyon (Paris)"},"to":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:61414","name":"Montereau (Montereau-Fault-Yonne)"}},{"lineId":"line:IDFM:C01731","from":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:73626","name":"Gare de Lyon (Paris)"},"to":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:411483","name":"Montargis (Montargis)"}},{"lineId":"line:IDFM:C01731","from":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:61414","name":"Montereau (Montereau-Fault-Yonne)"},"to":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:73626","name":"Gare de Lyon (Paris)"}},{"lineId":"line:IDFM:C01731","from":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:411483","name":"Montargis (Montargis)"},"to":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:73626","name":"Gare de Lyon (Paris)"}}],"disruption_id":"282071d8-a1e3-467e-ab40-9745924036c5"},{"id":"889e01e8-dfc5-42f0-9b9c-8b10b14c20b9","applicationPeriods":[{"begin":"20260429T172600","end":"20260507T235900"}],"lastUpdate":"20260429T174258","cause":"PERTURBATION","severity":"PERTURBEE","title":"Ligne J. Du 4 au 7 mai. Certains trains ne circulent pas.","message":"<p>Ligne J. Du lundi 4 au jeudi 7 mai, l&#8217;offre de transport est adapt&#233;e. Certains trains ne circulent pas. Ceci est la cons&#233;quence de l&#8217;incident d&#8217;exploitation rendant indisponibles certains trains. <br>D